Template: githaven/username
Type: string
Default: git
_Description: Dedicated account on the system for githaven:
 Repositories are managed by githaven under a single system account.
 Individual users login with ssh keys.  This user name is part
 of the url command users use to clone repositories such as
 "git clone git@example.com:foobar.git".
 .
 The account name can be customized but you should not use an existing
 account.

Template: githaven/directory
Type: string
Default: /var/git
_Description: Home directory for the user where git repositories and the website will be stored.
 Please specify the directory where githaven will manage store repositories and
 the web application's files
 .
 If you choose an already existing directory, this installation process
 will leave it unmodified.
